    <h2 class="section-title">The Skills Gap on Council Is Real.<br>I Can Fill It.</h2>
    <p class="section-intro">For over 15 years I've built a career at the intersection of marketing, communications, and technology — managing platforms, owning budgets, being accountable for results at companies across Canada, all while running a farm in Nipissing Township.</p>

    <div class="skills-grid">
