        <span class="career-role-co">Wave HQ · Jun 2023–Oct 2024</span>
        <p>Led the full marketing technology stack — strategy, vendor selection, implementation. Managed a team of 3, owned the budget, interfaced across 10+ departments.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="career-card" style="border-top-color: var(--pine-mid);">
        <div style="font-size:1.3rem;margin-bottom:0.7rem;">📱</div>
        <h3>Lifecycle Marketing Manager</h3>
        <span class="career-role-co">Nuula (formerly BFS Capital) · Nov 2020–Aug 2022</span>
        <p>Managed the full marketing technology stack for customer retention using Salesforce, Segment, Amplitude, Twilio, and more.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="callout callout--sand">
      <div class="callout-icon">💡</div>
      <div>
        <h4>What This Means for Nipissing Township</h4>
        <p>When the Township approved TownSuite at nearly twice the budget and six times the only other bidder, someone with my background would have asked: What's the implementation plan? Who's accountable for milestones? What are the exit criteria if this fails? I will ask these questions. Every time. Before we sign, not after we fail.</p>
